title: PML-N Amir Muqam wins NA-11 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) candidate, Amir Muqam has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-11, Shangla by securing 59,863 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate, Syed Fareen who bagged 54,311 votes.
The votersâ€™ turn-out remained 32.61%.
